reviews.text: Very good all-u-can-eat dim sum lunch 🍵🥢🍜🥟🍲🥠
Nice dining environment, good services & fairly decent Chinese food being served & even better if a bit less oily. Fairly good value here.

Cozy place and good service. Their booth seats are spacious and with high privacy so you can enjoy your nwal and chit chat with your friends freely. Dim Sum taste good and the presentation is also very decent. The all you can seat set might be a little bit pricey but worth to try.

We enjoyed a great family celebration at this place! ❤️ 
All-you-can-eat type yum-cha brunch with dishes carefully prepared according to our requests: portion / ways to separate different ingredients e.g. meat from vegetables etc. (But of course it could have been even better if there are more veggie options.)
The Manager sent us some steamed peach buns on the house specially for the birthday guy! Nth can beat great services!
Delicate Chinese cuisine, nice ambience, nice  servant

reviews.text: Happy hour 5-9pm 7 days a week! Love the outdoor area away from the band. 5-star service and great selection of wine. Not so much of a people watching bar, but a nice spot to hang out with friends over good wine.
Love this bar. Nothing is too much for the friendly staff. Happy hour two beers for the price of one.
Live band good quality. Price is  bargain for quality red wine. Good environment

It's not bad, but not fantastic. To be fair, its a great bar with live performance. Just that in TST, where you are so spoilt for choice, there's nothing really that allows it to stand out from the crowd.
Nice ambience and above average service. Has live music and a good singer.

result.name: 請請吧

reviews.text: Happy hour 5-9pm 7 days a week! Love the outdoor area away from the band. 5-star service and great selection of wine. Not so much of a people watching bar, but a nice spot to hang out with friends over good wine.
地點方便適中，環境開揚舒適，以酒店所屬酒吧而言，消費合理，食物飲品質素亦有所保證。
環境舒適，晚上9:00後有現場獻唱。

如果淨系睇個英文，仲以為系『錢錢吧』，知道叫『請請吧』後，又感到細路仔。

到訪幾次，一次比一次早有人唱歌，不過想靜靜地傾下偈，不妨到室外坐。

Happy hour 到九點，買一送一。叫杯紅酒，佢真係會倒半杯畀你，話曬都係酒店酒的質素確實有返咁上下，小吃如花生、蝦條，可以無限添食。

お酒の好きな香港人に勧められて行ってみました。落ち着いた高級な雰囲気にも関わらず、お値段は意外とリーズナブル。
店内では生演奏が楽しめます。落ち着いて話したいときは、テラス席がおすすめです。
